Key Match Events: Jos Buttler was named Player of the Match
Post-Match Reflections: Kane Williamson commented on England's performance and New Zealand's defeat
Jos Buttler shared his thoughts on England's victory and their chances in the tournament
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was played in the ICC Men's T20 World Cup 2022-23
The match was played at the Brisbane Cricket Ground, Woolloongabba, Brisbane
Others: Jos Buttler scored 73 runs and Alex Hales scored 52 runs for England
Sam Curran took 2 wickets for England and Chris Woakes also took 2 wickets
Glenn Phillips scored 62 runs for New Zealand
